show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/S7py8q
show.description: After being betrayed and left to die by the man she loved, Priya is mysteriously sent back eight years in time. Now, with knowledge of the future, she plots revenge against those who destroyed her—starting with her ex-fiancé Arjun.
